  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下教育平台的核心服务流转。从课堂服务开始，老师发起课程后，数据会先流向LMS门户。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以ClassroomService是起点，箭头指向LMS Portal。这个LMS门户是老师管理课程的后台入口对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，但这里有个细节——LMS Portal处理完请求后，会回调ClassroomService来同步课堂状态。所以这里有个双向循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在LMS Portal后面加了一条线回到ClassroomService，标记状态同步。接下来呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "状态同步完成后，ClassroomService会再次确认，这次确认是为了触发学生数据的查询。需要再连一次ClassroomService作为中间节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "所以是C节点，又一个ClassroomService？这是同一个服务实例还是表示不同的处理阶段？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是处理阶段，可以理解为二次确认后的查询动作。从这个节点要连到StudentDB获取学生名单。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加StudentDB节点。学生数据拿到之后，下一步是成绩相关的处理吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，StudentDB的数据会送到GradeSync服务，这是专门处理成绩同步的模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "GradeSync已加上。这个服务需要两步处理吗？我看到流程比较长。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，GradeSync内部有个分发逻辑，第一步接收成绩数据，第二步按课程分类后回传。所以需要两个GradeSync节点串联。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，第二个GradeSync处理完后，数据要回到哪里？LMS Portal吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，成绩最终要展示在LMS Portal上，让老师查看。所以第二个GradeSync连回LMS Portal。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，LMS Portal这里已经是第二次出现了。接下来还有内容分发的环节吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有，LMS Portal渲染页面时需要加载课件资源，要连到ContentCDN获取静态内容。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "ContentCDN已添加。这个CDN节点之后流程就结束了吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "不，这里要形成一个闭环。ContentCDN加载完成后，整个课堂服务流程才算就绪，所以要连回最开始的ClassroomService。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "闭环回到A节点的ClassroomService？这样整个流程就是一个循环了，每次课堂会话都走这一圈？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，这是一个完整的课堂生命周期循环。不过让我再检查一下——从B到C这里，我之前说的是LMS Portal回调ClassroomService，但方向有没有画反？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "确认一下，B是LMS Portal，C是ClassroomService，箭头从B指向C，表示Portal回调服务，这个方向是对的。需要调整吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "方向没问题，是我多虑了。整体结构就这样，ClassroomService起点，经过Portal、数据库、成绩同步、CDN，最后回到起点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，整个闭环流程已确认完成。九个节点，从A到I再回到A，涵盖了课堂服务、门户、数据库、成绩同步和内容分发的完整链路。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
